{"tid":365800,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[勿相認] 啱先玩first impression","createTime":"2017-08-19T13:38:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T14:52:16.000Z","uid":137977,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bebe1be00249a9e93b084cc7c4bb3620d19e6cf6","tid":365800,"uid":137977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T13:38:21.000Z","msg":"今日開始入營(時間唔好深究、勿起底 <br />\n一入營無耐破冰緊係玩First impression架啦<br />\n話哂個個都唔識大家 <br />\n由呢個活動破冰好正常<br />\n<br />\n點知有條個樣毒毒地既毒撚<br />\n一開始就比人投哂日日打飛機、<br />\n小學讀特殊學校(因為佢個樣真係樣衰到成個智障咁<br />\n睇住佢由玩之前笑哂口好開心個樣<br />\n變到黑哂臉眼紅紅咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住又有件豬西比人投成世嫁唔出、花名叫如花<br />\n成班人指住佢細聲講大聲笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢即刻轉身出左去喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果陣我已經心諗佢地會唔會quit camp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住無幾耐有人問先果兩「件」去左邊<br />\n就已經唔見左佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都多謝佢地真係好有效帶動到成個ocamp氣氛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8212917319ba8697a8480f547d53b60ee01c409e","tid":365800,"uid":137977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T13:38:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0d45fe613a02eeeb5e15c3733f4c19caf134cc","tid":365800,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T14:23:05.000Z","msg":"針"},{"pid":"58752c85c402db853c78efc50b21a7f174a869fd","tid":365800,"uid":25313,"like":2,"dislike":0,